    "description": "检查新的<strong>DLC，免费的</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/Without_name-1.jpg?t=1671787688\" /></span><br><br><strong>《山羊的故事2》</strong>是一款精准平台游戏，是第一部分非常受欢迎的续集（<strong>在Steam上有超过4万次下载和84%的好评！</strong>）。与前作一样，玩家的主要目标是登上顶峰，但由于采用了全新的机制以及改进的物理学，这项任务应该更容易一些。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概述</h2><br>-<strong>新机制</strong><br>游戏中加入了许多新的机制，比如气流，我们勇敢的山羊可以在四个方向上移动。或者是特殊的岩石架，她可以抓住岩石架悄悄地滑下来，而不会被墙弹开。还增加了更多的图形效果，例如，玩家可以在两种图形调色板之间进行选择。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/2480b76aded853c74388ad2134b7a6ae.poster.avif?t=1671787688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/2480b76aded853c74388ad2134b7a6ae.webm?t=1671787688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/2480b76aded853c74388ad2134b7a6ae.mp4?t=1671787688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>-<strong>世界探索</strong>。<br>山羊的故事2》比前作更强调探索。在每个阶段，你可以找到埋藏的宝物或Npc，他们会建议你如何越过更困难的跳跃，并为他们的帮助投下一分钱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/a96c62803d4671bde192802fb222d3de.poster.avif?t=1671787688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/a96c62803d4671bde192802fb222d3de.webm?t=1671787688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/a96c62803d4671bde192802fb222d3de.mp4?t=1671787688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>-<strong>与朋友合作</strong>。<br>游戏有一个全新的模式，允许你在通过关卡时一起合作。第二个玩家扮演一个特殊的帮手，他可以搭起平台，让第一个玩家跳上去，从而更容易通过游戏中比较困难的阶段。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/42870d88df4a9a604faa0f26845e3821.poster.avif?t=1671787688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/42870d88df4a9a604faa0f26845e3821.webm?t=1671787688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065630/extras/42870d88df4a9a604faa0f26845e3821.mp4?t=1671787688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《山羊的故事2》是：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>一个新的更大的冒险</strong>。<br><br></li><li> <strong>更多的沉浸式游戏玩法</strong>。<br><br></li><li> <strong>伟大的音乐</strong>。<br><br></li><li> <strong>与朋友的乐趣。</strong>。<br><br></li><li> <strong>美丽的像素艺术图形。</strong>。<br><br></li><li> <strong>只挑战最好的玩家。</strong>。<br></li></ul>",
